{"tid":1136340,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡卓妍 卓韻芝 正印小三爭奪之戰「舞台劇《情敵勸退師》」討論區","createTime":"2019-05-03T02:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T17:30:35.000Z","uid":242050,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ece05d74509efb560dd9e91a409ec8442d936112","tid":1136340,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/is3LULC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fis3LULC.png&h=72facb28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【《情敵勸退師》5月3日起接受優先訂票 <a href=\"http://www.schoolmatestheatre.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.schoolmatestheatre.com&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=ace757ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.schoolmatestheatre.com</a>】<br />\n<br />\n蔡卓妍・卓韻芝閨密內鬨<br />\n凌文龍・胡麗英・張銘耀推波助攻<br />\ntbc...原創舞台劇場《情敵勸退師》<br />\n<br />\n情人出軌，我哋有計！<br />\n幫你趕走情敵，不成功不收費！<br />\n<br />\n陳淑儀導演・郭翠怡編劇・張珮華監製<br />\n作家陳煩同名系列前傳故事<br />\n<br />\n8月演藝學院 正式開業 以退為愛<br />\n5月3日開始接受預約 一齊笑退小三 「有⼩三？唔怕！搵『情敵勸退師』啦。我哋專業嘅團隊會幫你同你嘅伴侶杜絕第三者嘅侵害、維護⽇久失修嘅愛情⋯⋯」「她」（蔡卓妍飾）聽到收音機的廣告，立即收起那⼀公升眼淚與鼻⽔，像看到救世主⼀樣雙眼閃閃發光。終於，「她」立定決⼼誓要與⼩三（卓韻芝飾）來⼀個終極對決，⼆話不說向「情敵勸退事務所」拔足狂奔。「情敵勸退事務所」創立人⽊村（張銘耀飾），帶領多年好友 Charlotte（胡麗英飾）及年青員⼯樂少（凌文龍飾）立即開展調查，發現這名外遇不單是⼩三，更是前度！<br />\n<br />\ntbc...原創舞台劇場《情敵勸退師》優先訂票資料<br />\n<br />\n演出日期／時間：2019年8月10&ndash;11日及15-18⽇/晚八時 　2019年8⽉11及18⽇/下午三時<br />\n地點： 香港演藝學院歌劇院<br />\n門票： $560(堂座),$460(樓座)# <br />\n優先訂票日期： 2019年5月3日開始<br />\n優先訂票網址： <a href=\"http://www.schoolmatestheatre.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.schoolmatestheatre.com&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=ace757ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.schoolmatestheatre.com</a> (設網上平台、下載表格或以 Whatsapp 訂票方式) *另設$280、$180及$680 (限量貴賓票)以及設全日制學生、長者及殘疾人士優惠，但均不作優先訂票，公開售票詳情請密切留意公佈。<br />\n<br />\n主辦：太陽娛樂亞洲、tbc...<br />\n主辦及製作：同窗文化"},{"pid":"69e20697419cab4ee8e58a5977e02362e113ed01","tid":1136340,"uid":242050,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:49:54.000Z","msg":"優先購票： 8月18日 晚上8點 VIP$680貴賓票<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">售罄</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴絲買到飛？"},{"pid":"6cf0753d531d071cf6e6ae9f8d537cd030ddc17b","tid":1136340,"uid":185779,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:14:54.000Z","msg":"阿Sa講嘢一舊舊, 咬字不清點做舞台劇"},{"pid":"7e066962b093520e72c34f4cb6ac6f1d7325317b","tid":1136340,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cf0753d531d071cf6e6ae9f8d537cd030ddc17b","tid":1136340,"uid":185779,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:14:54.000Z","msg":"阿Sa講嘢一舊舊, 咬字不清點做舞台劇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"可能佢今次嘅角色本身講野都係一舊舊呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5f43bbc046e9db167c6fbf5a6cdcab8f664fdb","tid":1136340,"uid":81562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:21:41.000Z","msg":"正印同小學生爭寵？"},{"pid":"19e8ba1d4ea498ebe404f2f388ab45954e36c151","tid":1136340,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ef5f43bbc046e9db167c6fbf5a6cdcab8f664fdb","tid":1136340,"uid":81562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:21:41.000Z","msg":"正印同小學生爭寵？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:19:17.000Z","msg":"好似阿Sa先係演正印嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175cae07d1dffc5f6ada34023f947cea70bccc54","tid":1136340,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:40:04.000Z","msg":"VIP飛賣曬啦 好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee39e5ee0c81e71c3e3b40ecd